snippet.title: Bee Simulator – Gamescom 2018 Trailer (PC, Xbox One, PS4, Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Add Bee Simulator to your Steam wishlist!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/914750/Bee_Simulator/
Stay tuned:
www.beesimulator.com
FB: https://www.facebook.com/BeeSimulator/ 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/beesimulatorgame/?hl=pl 
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSLhlSibAfN4dRkKb2JIE4g 

Bee Simulator is coming to PC, Xbox One, PS4 and Nintendo Switch!
See the world through the eyes of a bee! Compete with other bees in races, collect pollen, perform waggle dances, and explore a world inspired by Central Park in New York. Play it with your family or friends, choosing between three modes, including co-op and vs. split-screen.
